<ul class=3D"toc-indentation">=20
<li><a href=3D"#InstallationGuideforUnix-BasedSystems-1.InstallaLAMPStack(*=
NIX,Apache,MySQL,PHP5+)">1. Install a LAMP Stack (*NIX, Apache, MySQL, PHP5=
+)</a></li>=20
<li><a href=3D"#InstallationGuideforUnix-BasedSystems-2.GetComposer">2. Get=
 Composer</a></li>=20
<li><a href=3D"#InstallationGuideforUnix-BasedSystems-3.Downloadthedesiredv=
